or pentagon area, apothem, perimeter, and many more</h2>
<div class=3D"textBlock"><p>To calculate any pentagon characteristic, we on=
ly need to know its side length (<code>a</code>)</p>
</div><div class=3D"tableBlock"><table class=3D"tableBlock__table-striped t=
